**Name:** alertaLaboralTrigger  
**Schedule expression:** `cron(0 8 ? * 3 *)`  
**Description:** Executes the Lambda function every Wednesday at 08:00 UTC (10:00 Madrid time)  
**Target:** Lambda function (`alertaLaboralHandler`)  
**Purpose:** Weekly check for new job offers based on user-defined keywords
